cl-oracle - Price Oracle Framework
===================================

This project contains code extracted and adapted from CLPIC
(Common Lisp P2P Intellectual Property Chain).

Original source files:
- src/oracle/package.lisp
- src/oracle/core/types.lisp
- src/oracle/feeds/price.lisp
- src/oracle/aggregation/median.lisp

The code has been refactored into a standalone library with:
- No external dependencies (pure Common Lisp)
- Simplified API focused on price feed aggregation
- Removed blockchain-specific functionality
- Removed cryptographic signing requirements

For the full oracle network implementation including VRF,
attestations, staking, and blockchain integration, see the
original CLPIC project.
